Please note that the game logic for exploration, reproduction, resource collection, and upgrades is not implemented in this example. You'll need to implement these features according to your game design and requirements.

Once you've set up these files, you can run your Flask application by executing `python game_app.py` in your terminal or command prompt. This will start a local development server, and you can access the game in your web browser at `http://127.0.0.1:5000/`.
